Plugin to allow migrations for Symfony 1.4 projects with multiple databases


== Installation ==

Just copy plugin files to plugins/ directory and clear cache

== Use ==

task <pre>multiDBmigration:generate</pre> 
* checks differences between schema and model
* Generate a migration classes in /lib/migration/<classConnectionName>

task <pre>multiDBmigration:migrate</pre> 
* checks version of all databases and migration classes
* applies changes to all databases accordingly


